# CSS & Design System

## Layout

- **Nav**: Fixed left, `top: 9rem`, column layout
- **Main**: `margin-left: 12rem` to clear nav
- **Header**: Centered title with gradient underline

## Color Palette

| Token | Value | Use |
|-------|-------|-----|
| Background | `#201c29` | Body |
| Primary accent | `#ab49de` | Title, gradients |
| Secondary | `#d39fee` | Nav links, underlines, content text |

## Typography

- Font: `Montserrat` (Google Fonts)
- Base: `62.5%` (10px equivalent)
- Title: `2rem`, uppercase
- Nav: `1.4rem`; active state `2rem`

## Content Sections

Shared pattern for `.content-section`, `.profile-container`, `.rendered-content`:

- `::before` pseudo: radial gradient background
- `border-radius: 15px`, `box-shadow`
- `.profile-container`: flex, space-evenly (GitHub + PDF widgets)

## Nav Animation

- `.nav-link.active`: absolute positioning, `translate(-50%, -50%)`, `2rem` font
- `::before` on links: gradient underline, `scaleX(0.1)` default, `scaleX(1)` on hover/active
- Transition: `0.5s` for position/opacity
